exceptions.exn: In environment U, V : NormedModule R_AbsRing f : R -> U * V a, b : R l : U * V H : is_RInt (fun t : R => fst (f t)) a b (fst l) Unable to unify "is_RInt (fun t : R => fst (f t)) a b (fst l)" with "is_RInt (fun t : R => snd (f t)) a b (snd l)".

original: intros. apply is_RInt_fct_extend_fst in H. simpl in H. apply H.
